  <div class="organisation__contact-section organisation__contact-section--border-top">
    <h3 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--font-size-19 gem-c-heading--padding  ">Reporting Fraud</h3>


    <div class="grid-row">

    </div>
    <p>The CICA is committed to preventing and tackling fraud to protect public funds intended for victims of violent crime. If you suspect someone has made a fraudulent claim for criminal injuries compensation, you can let us know in strict confidence by emailing us on <a href="mailto:fraud@cica.gov.uk" class="brand__color">fraud@cica.gov.uk</a>.</p>
  </div>

</section>


